Interface AsymmetricMeter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    OpenemsComponent, SymmetricMeter
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MeterCarloGavazziEm300, SinglePhaseMeter, SocomecMeter, SocomecMeterSinglephase, SocomecMeterThreephase
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSunSpecMeter, DummyAsymmetricMeter, FeneconDessGridMeter, FeneconDessPvMeter, FeneconProPvMeter, GoodWeEtGridMeter, GridMeter, GridMeter, MeterAbbB23Mbus, MeterArtemesAM2, MeterBControlEM300, MeterCarloGavazziEm300Impl, MeterDiscovergy, MeterJanitzaUmg604, MeterJanitzaUmg96rme, MeterMicrocareSDM630, MeterPqplusUmd97, MeterSchneiderActi9Smartlink, NrcMeter, ProductionMeter, SocomecMeterSinglephaseImpl, SocomecMeterThreephaseImpl, SolarEdgeGridMeter

    public interface AsymmetricMeter
extends SymmetricMeter
    Represents an Asymmetric Meter. - Negative ActivePowerL1/L2/L3 and ConsumptionActivePowerL1/L2/L3 represent Consumption, i.e. power that is 'leaving the system', e.g. feed-to-grid - Positive ActivePowerL1/L2/L3 and ProductionActivePowerL1/L2/L3 represent Production, i.e. power that is 'entering the system', e.g. buy-from-grid
